{"title":"太阳的恩泽","authors":["赵贵辰"],"dates":[{"year":1990,"month":4,"day":6}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"太阳的恩泽"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赵贵辰"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大地伸着海一样的手"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把太阳举到"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"驱散黑暗的地方"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"太阳把光芒全给了大地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就这样"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当我作为一棵秧苗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"长成秋天后"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还能感谢谁呢"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一粒粒粮食"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"喷发阳光味"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"被历史咀嚼着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一篇《为人民服务》"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把党群关系变成鱼、水"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"美丽了泉流飞瀑般的中国革命"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如果我们把它忘记了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"难道那贪婪的苍蝇还不来吗"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}